cipher = "fdisk pzkx"
shift = 6

plain_text = ""

for char in cipher:
    if char.isalpha():
        shift_char = chr(((ord(char.lower()) - 97 - shift) % 26) + 97)
        plain_text += shift_char if char.islower() else shift_char.upper()
    else:
        plain_text += char

print(plain_text)
